            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-7add56b5-d26b-4a58-8159-d2868a199d5c">
                Mr. Shurmer  (Birmingham, Sparkbrook)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-7add56b5-d26b-4a58-8159-d2868a199d5c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
