        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-368e0206-142f-4017-81e1-e4eed24db081">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-368e0206-142f-4017-81e1-e4eed24db081">
                Vice-Admiral Taylor  (Paddington, South)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-368e0206-142f-4017-81e1-e4eed24db081" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
