                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">How many unemployed were there under the Socialist Government in 1930? Give the figures to the House.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
